                        <interp inst="t18370508-name-820" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE BALL</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable N</hi> 70.) I saw the prisoner running, and saw him throw down the bag which contained this sheet-copper. I ran and took him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
